data.description:
Step into luxury with this beautifully remodeled 4-bedroom, 3-bath haven. Natural light floods in through every room, accentuating the functional layout of this centrally located gem. The inviting living room seamlessly connects to a well-appointed kitchen and spacious dining area. Privacy is key, with the master suite strategically placed on the opposite side of the bedrooms.But the real showstopper? A brand-new travertine pool deck, complete with a jacuzzi and a sparkling saltwater pool for your ultimate enjoyment. Venture into the expansive backyard (0.42 acres), offering space for toys, the potential for a new business venture, and even a small NEW Turf Dog Park(45x15). This home is a perfect blend of style, comfort, and endless possibilities. Don't let this dream slip away! Even better this is a double lot LOTS 59 & 60!! Replaced the oversized Septic Tank, New Large Fence, New Pool and Spa, Added a second AC in the flex room with laundry, New Driveway and back millings parking space, 6 Ring Outdoor Flood Light cameras system, New Turf Dog Park 45x15, New Gutters Front and Back, and Newer Electric Tankless Water Heater. 

Just minutes away from Downtown Daytona Beach, The World's Most Famous Beach, NASCAR races at Daytona International Speedway, and endless outdoor activities including golfing, kayaking, deep-sea fishing, jet skiing and boating.  Don't miss this AMAZING opportunity and Call to schedule your private showing today!
